The paper deals with the formal verification of a security service, specifically Remote Attestation, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the design and evaluation of a hardware-software co-design, which could be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper involves the use of hardware, which could be categorized under computer architecture (cs.AR) and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
